"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-arts-entertainment-tv-news-vatican-olympics-last-supper-paris-b2591509.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The opening ceremony's sketch has drawn backlash despite the artistic director explaining that the scene was intended to recreate the 'Feast of Dionysus'  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  TheVaticanhas joined the chorus of critics condemning theParis 2024Olympics for featuring a sketch in its opening ceremony that hasbeen interpreted as parodyingThe Last Supper.\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the prestigious event held along the Seine River on July 26, a scene was featured showing drag queens, a transgender model, a naked singer dressed up as the Greek god of wine Dionysus, and a child together at a long dining table.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9956583117783044, \"rank\": 0.004140069099228467, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 861, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8830781604995263e-19, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The moment has drawn backlash from the Catholic Church and others, includingFull Housestar Candace Cameron Bure who accused it of beinga \\\"disgusting\\\" and \\\"blasphemous\\\" recreation ofLeonardo da Vinci's famous paintingof Jesus Christ and his apostles sharing a final meal before his crucifixion.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9992127723159377, \"rank\": 0.0007873189739060302, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 1136, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999742883600843, \"rank\": 2.5712300667352862e-05, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the Olympics artistic director Thomas Jollyaffirming that he was inspired by Jan van Bijlert'sFeast of Dionysuspainting, the Vatican has now joined the voices deploring the \\\"offense.\\\"\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9999991986468131, \"rank\": 7.14177389915956e-07, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jan van Bijlert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Holy See was saddened by certain scenes at the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympic Games and cannot but join the voices raised in recent days to deplore the offense done to many Christians and believers of other religions,\\\" it said in a press release shared on Saturday, August 3.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1590, \"end\": 1600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9874636969566397, \"rank\": 0.01182155309558123, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At a prestigious event where the whole world comes together to share common values, there should be no allusions ridiculing the religious convictions of many people.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The freedom of expression, which is clearly not called into question here, is limited by respect for others.\\\"\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the outcry from various figures and viewers,Olympic organizers explained that the decision to include the sketch was motivated by a desire to achieve \\\"community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(The opening ceremony) tried to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps told a press conference.\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2301, \"end\": 2311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9398742011576491e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2330, \"end\": 2338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense, we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2459, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 president Tony Estanguet also said: \\\"We imagined a ceremony to show our values and our principles so we gave a very committed message.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2461, \"end\": 2471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9398742011576491e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea was to really trigger a reflection.\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We wanted to have a message as strong as possible.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch Apple TV+ free for 7 day  New subscribers only.\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a39.99/mo.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"after free trial.\", \"from\":